name: Samurai Dude-Jirō 地郎-PE
description:
A young man called Jirō means a rascal son who love in the ground, he was became a general and serving for his lord daimyō, you maybe think he is a good man, but don't be easy with him, while in the battlefield he can deceive when he is facing his enemies.
